# hpt_pipeline.dag — Full HP tuning pipeline as a DAGMan workflow
#
# Automates the complete workflow from Episode 6:
#   1. PREP:    Prepare train/val/test splits from raw CSV
#   2. SWEEP:   Run all HP trials in parallel
#   3. AGG:     Aggregate results and identify best config
#   4. RETRAIN: Retrain best model on train+val, evaluate on test
#
# Submit with: condor_submit_dag hpt_pipeline.dag

JOB PREP    prep_data.sub
JOB SWEEP   hpt_sweep.sub
JOB AGG     aggregate.sub
JOB RETRAIN retrain_best.sub

PARENT PREP    CHILD SWEEP
PARENT SWEEP   CHILD AGG
PARENT AGG     CHILD RETRAIN

RETRY SWEEP   2
RETRY RETRAIN 1
